020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200210152715/https://www.todayonline.com/singapore/novel-coronavirus-3-new-cases-confirmed-all-have-not-recently-travelled-china|archive-date=10 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> the 10 Seletar Aerospace Heights construction site, the [[Grace Assembly of God]],<ref name=\"13FebMOH\">{{cite web |title=Eight More Confirmed Cases of COVID-19 Infection |work=MOH |url=https://www.moh.gov.sg/news-highlights/details/eight-more-confirmed-cases-of-covid-19-infection |accessdate=13 February 2020 |date=13 February 2020 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200213114302/https://www.moh.gov.sg/news-highlights/details/eight-more-confirmed-cases-of-covid-19-infection |archive-date=13 February 2020 |url-status=dead }}</ref> Wizlearn Technologies (an e-learning firm at [[Singapore Science Park]]),<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/new-coronavirus-cluster-at-e-learning-company-in-science-park-ii-with-4-staff|title=New coronavirus cluster at company in Science Park II with 4 staff infected, including 2 new cases announced|last1=Goh|first1=Timothy|last2=Kaur|first2=Karamjit|date=28 February 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=28 February 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228123937/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/new-coronavirus-cluster-at-e-learning-company-in-science-park-ii-with-4-staff|archive-date=28 February 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> a private singing event at [[SAFRA National Service Association|SAFRA]] Jurong,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/5-new-covid-19-cases-in-spore-including-4-linked-to-a-new-cluster-a-private-dinner|title=5 new Covid-19 cases in S'pore: 4 linked to new cluster involving Safra Jurong private dinner|last1=Choo|first1=Yun Ting|date=5 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=5 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200305215650/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/5-new-covi