al salon|last1=Yuen|first1=Sin|date=29 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=29 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200329130533/https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/42-new-coronavirus-patients-in-singapore-3-cases-form-new-cluster-in-yishun-bridal-salon|archive-date=29 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> S11 Dormitory\u200a\u200a@\u200a\u200aPunggol, the Wilby Residences, Hero's,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/35-new-covid-19-cases-in-spore-3-new-clusters-a-bar-in-circular-road-a-dormitory-at|title=35 new Covid-19 cases in S'pore, 3 new clusters - a bar in Circular Road, a dormitory in Seletar North Link and a serviced apartment in Wilby Road|last1=Yong|first1=Clement|date=30 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=30 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200331042048/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/35-new-covid-19-cases-in-spore-3-new-clusters-a-bar-in-circular-road-a-dormitory-at|archive-date=31 March 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Westlite Toh Guan dormitory,<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/coronavirus-new-covid-19-cluster-at-westlite-toh-guan-dormitory-linked-to-5-cases|title=86-year-old resident of old age home among 47 new Covid-19 cases in Singapore|last1=Toh|first1=Ting Wei|date=31 March 2020|website=The Straits Times|accessdate=31 March 2020|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200401051927/http://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/health/coronavirus-new-covid-19-cluster-at-westlite-toh-guan-dormitory-linked-to-5-cases|archive-date=1 April 2020|url-status=live}}</ref> Lee Ah Mooi Old Age Home, the 55 Sungei Kadut Loop dormitory,<ref>{{cite web |last1=Yong |first1=Clement |url=https://www.straitstimes.com/singapore/74-new-coronavirus-cases-in-spore-bringing-total-to-1000-54-new-cases-are-local-with-10 |title=Coronavirus cases in S'pore hit 1,000 with 74 new patients; 10 cases from old folks' home, including a 102-year-old |website=The Straits 